narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Yes, sources were available - readings were on classes v2. Again, a presentation schedule (with make up classes, etc) accessible for reference would have been nice.
No. The library policy of one book for one day is total shit, as always.
